  "texts": [
    "These models also support instance-level understanding, enabling visual referring and grounding.",
    "For referring, GPT4RoI (Zhang et al. 2024a) and Position-Enhanced Visual Instruction Tuning (Chen et al.",
    "2023a) map text prompts to specific regions.",
    "For grounding, Kosmos-2 (Peng et al. 2023b) and Grounding-DINO (Liu et al.",
    "2024) combine box-level detection with grounded pretraining."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}